# Optional: privacy-first, anonymous usage analytics via GoatCounter.
# Leave this UNSET and the app makes zero outbound requests (default).
# Set it to your GoatCounter "count" endpoint to enable visitor + event counts.
# Only anonymous page paths and event names are sent — never document content.
# Users can still opt out in Settings, and Do Not Track is always respected.
#
# VITE_GOATCOUNTER_URL=https://YOURCODE.goatcounter.com/count
